title: Beth Tikkun Study in Genesis
description:
Enjoy this insightful study into the Book of Genesis from a Messianic Hebraic 

perspective. Grant Luton offers a fantastic study into God's Word, utilizing his 

God given Knowledge & Wisdom in unraveling the written word. You will enjoy his 

teaching style and come away blessed.
Weekly teachings are held at Beth Tikkun Messianic Fellowship
MP3 & PDF files
"So then faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God."
